    "cff_info": "<div id=\"fieldInfoIsCHEMiA\" style=\" margin-top: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px;\">\n  <h4>IsCHEMiA Score</h4>\n  <p><i>Leung WCY et al., 2026 (Neurology)</i></p>\n  <p><b>DOI:</b>\n    <a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1212/WNL.0000000000214486\" target=\"_blank\">\n      10.1212/WNL.0000000000214486\n    </a>\n  </p>\n  <p><b>Citation:</b>\n    Leung WCY, Tanaka T, Donahue RA, et al. Development and International Validation of a Novel Imaging-Based Risk Score (IsCHEMiA) for the Prediction of Poststroke Epilepsy. <i>Neurology</i>. 2026;106:e214486. doi:10.1212/WNL.0000000000214486\n  </p>\n  <h4>What it predicts</h4>\n  <p>\n    <b>Poststroke epilepsy (PSE):</b> occurrence or recurrence of an <b>unprovoked seizure &gt;7 days</b> after ischemic stroke.\n    Overall PSE incidence in the combined cohorts: <b>5.5%</b>.\n  </p>\n  <h4>Factors and Points (0–9 total)</h4>\n  <ul>\n    <li><b>(Is) Infarct size (largest dimension):</b>\n      <ul>\n        <li>&lt;5 cm: 0 points</li>\n        <li>≥5 cm: 2 points</li>\n      </ul>\n    </li>\n    <li><b>(C) Cortical involvement:</b>\n      <ul>\n        <li>No: 0 points</li>\n        <li>Yes: 1 point</li>\n      </ul>\n    </li>\n    <li><b>(H) Hemorrhagic transformation (any radiologic grade):</b>\n      <ul>\n        <li>No: 0 points</li>\n        <li>Yes: 2 points</li>\n      </ul>\n    </li>\n    <li><b>(E) Early seizures ≤7 days after stroke:</b>\n      <ul>\n        <li>No: 0 points</li>\n        <li>Yes: 2 points</li>\n      </ul>\n    </li>\n    <li><b>(Mi) MCA territory involvement:</b>\n      <ul>\n        <li>No: 0 points</li>\n        <li>Yes: 1 point</li>\n      </ul>\n    </li>\n    <li><b>(A) Age:</b>\n      <ul>\n        <li>≥65 years: 0 points</li>\n        <li>&lt;65 years: 1 point</li>\n      </ul>\n    </li>\n  </ul>\n  <h4>Risk Estimates by IsCHEMiA Score (Predicted PSE risk, 95% CI)</h4>\n  <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: flex-start;\">\n    <div style=\"flex: 1; min-width: 280px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 6px 0;\"><b>1-year risk</b></p>\n      <table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n        <thead>\n          <tr style=\"background-color: #f2f2f2;\">\n            <th style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">IsCHEMiA</th>\n            <th style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Risk</th>\n          </tr>\n        </thead>\n        <tbody>\n          <tr><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">0</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">0%</td></tr>\n          <tr><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">1</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">0% (0–1)</td></tr>\n          <tr><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">2</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">1% (1–2)</td></tr>\n          <tr><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">3</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">2% (1–4)</td></tr>\n          <tr><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">4</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">8% (6–11)</td></tr>\n          <tr><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">5</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">7% (4–12)</td></tr>\n          <tr><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">6</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">18% (12–24)</td></tr>\n          <tr><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">7</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">21% (12–33)</td></tr>\n          <tr><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">≥8</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">67% (23–90)</td></tr>\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"flex: 1; min-width: 280px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 6px 0;\"><b>5-year risk</b></p>\n      <table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;\">\n        <thead>\n          <tr style=\"background-color: #f2f2f2;\">\n            <th style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">IsCHEMiA</th>\n            <th style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Risk</th>\n          </tr>\n        </thead>\n        <tbody>\n          <tr><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">0</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">2% (0–4)</td></tr>\n          <tr><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">1</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">1% (0–1)</td></tr>\n          <tr><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">2</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">2% (1–3)</td></tr>\n          <tr><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">3</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">6% (4–9)</td></tr>\n          <tr><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">4</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">15% (11–19)</td></tr>\n          <tr><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">5</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">22% (15–30)</td></tr>\n          <tr><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">6</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">28% (20–37)</td></tr>\n          <tr><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">7</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">47% (32–60)</td></tr>\n          <tr><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">≥8</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">78% (25–96)</td></tr>\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">\n    <b>Examples reported in the paper:</b>\n    IsCHEMiA <b>=3</b> → <b>2%</b> (1-year) and <b>6%</b> (5-year) risk;\n    IsCHEMiA <b>≥8</b> → <b>67%</b> (1-year) and <b>78%</b> (5-year) risk.\n  </p>\n  <h4>Clinical Utility</h4>\n  <p>\n    IsCHEMiA is a practical <b>imaging-based bedside</b> tool using routinely available CT/MRI and basic clinical data.\n    It showed strong discrimination across international cohorts and <b>outperformed SeLECT</b> in the overall population,\n    supporting risk-informed counseling, follow-up planning, and trial enrichment.\n  </p>\n  <h4>Additional Study Information</h4>\n  <table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 10px;\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr style=\"background-color: #f2f2f2;\">\n        <th style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Category</th>\n        <th style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Details</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\"><b>Score Name</b></td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">IsCHEMiA (0–9 points)</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\"><b>Population</b></td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">\n          <b>Derivation (US):</b> MGH, n=1,436 (Jan 1, 2016 – Dec 31, 2018)<br>\n          <b>External validation:</b> 3 cohorts, total n=2,534<br>\n            • HK-QMH, n=1,286 (Aug 1, 2018 – Dec 31, 2022)<br>\n            • HK-RH, n=272 (Sep 1, 2019 – Jul 31, 2022)<br>\n            • Japan (NCVC), n=976 (Nov 1, 2014 – Sep 1, 2019)<br>\n          <b>Total:</b> n=3,970\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\"><b>Outcome Definition</b></td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">\n          Poststroke epilepsy (PSE): unprovoked seizure &gt;7 days after stroke.\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\"><b>Statistical Methods</b></td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">\n          Competing risk regression (mortality as competing event); backward stepwise elimination using AIC.\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\"><b>Validation Methods</b></td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">\n          External validation in 3 cohorts using discrimination (c-statistics) and calibration (spline-based calibration; O/E ratio and integrated calibration index).\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\"><b>Performance Metrics</b></td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">\n          C-statistic: US 0.870; HK-QMH 0.852; HK-RH 0.857; Japan 0.826; <b>Overall 0.848</b><br>\n          Calibration reported as good at 1 and 3 years in the overall validation cohort.\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\"><b>Comparison</b></td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">\n          Outperformed SeLECT in the overall population (0.848 vs 0.782; z=5.170; p&lt;0.0001).\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\"><b>Generalizability</b></td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">\n          High (validated across international cohorts in Hong Kong and Japan).\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\"><b>Clinical Utility</b></td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">\n          Imaging-based bedside risk stratification to support counseling, follow-up planning, and trial enrichment after ischemic stroke.\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>",
    "authors": "Leung WC, Tanaka T, Donahue RA, et al.",
    "journal": "Neurology",
    "year": 2026,
    "outcome": "Development and International Validation of a Novel Imaging-Based Risk Score (IsCHEMiA) for the Prediction of Poststroke Epilepsy"
  },
